{"tid":1363533,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"支線任務：嶺南人集會罷免何君堯","createTime":"2019-07-25T08:04:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-25T19:10:47.000Z","uid":59815,"like":46,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"2341f1d3f0741045cacb11bbb812b63088b32529","tid":1363533,"uid":59815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T08:04:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GQ52V30.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGQ52V30.png&h=02bce5af&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n大西北大學做野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n「校友日2019」取消　嶺南人自組「Homecoming Day」<br />\n<br />\n母校屹立，風波不搖，然現任校董何君堯，其言行卻備受廣大市民唾棄，聲名狼藉，恥與為伍！若何續居我校校董之位，實讓我輩嶺南人蒙受污名，有損我校百年清譽。<br />\n<br />\n即使「校友日2019」因故取消，但回家之路從沒中斷！現號召一眾紅灰嶺南人於本週末7月27日回家一聚，向校方表達罷免何氏校董一職之訴求，以保母校光風。<br />\n<br />\n日期：2019年7月27日（星期六）<br />\n時間：上午11時至下午2時<br />\n地點：嶺南大學<br />\n<br />\n風雨無阻，727，回家！<br />\n<br />\n#不要黑校董<br />\n#罷免何君堯<br />\n#掃黑除惡<br />\n#保嶺存博<br />\n<br />\ntg：<a href=\"https://t.me/guardourlingnan\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fguardourlingnan&d=9aIS%2Fhk2hxf5w8hb7WAMURyAur%2Bbp9MVyOkMM5%2FMxDY%3D&h=ca1c54be\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/guardourlingnan</a>"},{"pid":"ddad5fd73e63c656cbb2ca166502b0bd2a726c85","tid":1363533,"uid":208452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T08:05:10.000Z","msg":"PUSH <br />\n《生於亂世，有種責任》<br />\n唔好意思阻阻大家，我地想幫香港人出書，想收集大家意見<br />\n<br />\n出一本屬於香港人嘅自由之書<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1359361\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1359361</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"c716e72e9ecf011f42b35e6f85d3f294f069d1f3","tid":1363533,"uid":167928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T08:08:04.000Z","msg":"事實上校董會吹佢唔脹 何君堯係政府委任"},{"pid":"a6d7add86029a47cb1102d8eb2a048fdf4ac0ddf","tid":1363533,"uid":201197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T08:12:46.000Z","